        <h4>HOW TO GENERATE A PAYMENT VOUCHER FOR DIRECTPAY</h4>
        <div>
            <ol>
                <li>Click on the <b>Search</b> Menu tab at the <b>Home</b> page.</li>
                <li>At the Main Search page, click on the <b>Payment</b> menu tab.</li>
                <li>Select the <b>Generate Payment Voucher</b> option from the drop down </li>
                <li>Click <b>Generate Voucher Code</b> to generate the payment Voucher code.</li>
                <li>Use the Voucher Code generated to make your <b>DirectPay</b> transaction at the bank.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
