                <li>At the Main Search page, click on the <b>Payment</b> menu tab.</li>
                <li>Select the <b>Check Payment Balance</b> option from the drop down list</li>
                <li>Enter <b>PIN Code</b> in the box.</li>
                <li>Click the <b>Check Balance</b> button to complete.</li>
            </ol>
